Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: SOF: topology: remove snd_sof_complete_pipeline()
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 61ad28ff6cf349c3e25f6c4a56ce4d140c003d19
